{"tid":1438713,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"你老母中央有個搵仔web page呀DLKH","createTime":"2019-08-10T00:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T00:37:00.000Z","uid":66294,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8e05a25f118bd7a4b8e3d12be3d92eeefd51b1d5","tid":1438713,"uid":66294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:29:18.000Z","msg":"請廣傳，朋友認識中央既人，可靠消息：<br />\n<br />\n各位手足，去夢遊時緊記做好保護措施，無時無刻都要戴口罩，隠去特徵。中央已經設立舉報平台：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.12339.gov.cn/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.12339.gov.cn%2F&d=8kP02BZom8b0sC5RUQuyVUUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=1336c111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.12339.gov.cn/</a><br />\n<br />\n表明要&lsquo;暴徒&rsquo;唔遮臉既相片，憑相片與回鄉証做核對就可以確認手足身份，只要出入中國海關都會有麻煩。就算你唔會返大陸都好，唔排除將來會用作抽後算帳用途。各位手足，麻煩好好保護自己，唔好掉以輕心。"},{"pid":"94d138eb9caf70aa10c8ed79ab079f65f5d1741c","tid":1438713,"uid":66294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:31:09.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"628eb2752e8be1b0325b385be9d5788fb1b948ae","tid":1438713,"uid":66294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:31:30.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"3e320b63c1c4518be423603f695ae731e9e3af60","tid":1438713,"uid":66294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:31:45.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"ae19d20b249ecdcf9bfeba3767faa45845e3f798","tid":1438713,"uid":66294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:32:00.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"68e13634215a605ffbf20e3fe190d2f3a7feb08b","tid":1438713,"uid":245760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:32:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d52b15e92f336d1491aef815e1f677a8fcf48d1","tid":1438713,"uid":21034,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:33:11.000Z","msg":"我覺得唔推好啲 <br />\n遮樣呢啲已經變基本<br />\n怕你推左上去只有更多人知有得舉報"},{"pid":"3deed47013ef3cd2ae4044f656acab31ce16e1b5","tid":1438713,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy